            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="31533583">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">赵武灵王一世英名，竟因为对亲情不够决绝，而落得饿死的下场。掌握重权是危险的</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-05-09 10:00</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                赵武灵王一世英名，竟因为对亲情不够决绝，而落得饿死的下场。掌握重权是危险的
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

